	(text "1.6 Swapped two screen wires for direct connection\n1.5 /RD & /WR to include /IORQ & A2, updated to 74AHCT32 and Voltage rails\n1.4 Added /IORQ to /RD and /WR signals to filter unnecessary signals\n1.3 Changed 74XX series chip to AHCT and supply voltage, updated C2 to 3v3 rail\n1.2 Reordered logic gates so easier to read\n1.1 Added the /WR pin through the gate"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 178.308 173.99 0)
